00:00:27.430 --> 00:00:29.910
Aapko aur bhi kisi cheez ke liye yaad kiya tha bahut

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:34.050
- Ji haan - Woh jo aapko case batayi thi na

00:00:34.050 --> 00:00:36.270
- Ji, ji - Aayiye Hum bata dein

00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:44.300
- Woh log Madras pahunch gaye hain - Achcha

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:49.550
