00:01:38.376 --> 00:01:40.724
- Jesopi? - Aaya kya?

00:01:40.724 --> 00:01:45.310
- Jesopi, haan Jesopi. - Jesopi. Woh sab wahin aakar ke rehne waale hain

00:01:45.310 --> 00:01:49.940
